:266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"8.5 全民三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e71eae7bd17cc94d3640d1ac8d469c0aa23f5a","tid":1398194,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"平時十號風都係咁返架啦<br />\n至多咪早一日留係醫院訓<br />\n唔好睇少醫護返工嘅決心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確好多老屎忽係藍絲<br />\n但亦好多黃絲和理非得過份<br />\n就睇尋日個醫護集會<br />\n又係淪為叫口號同開閃光燈<br />\n叫佢地衝都唔會啦，何況罷工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2df70fb8c35850fe15866d568342ebd349215a","tid":1398194,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}